[SPEAKER_00] kod duhovnih ljudi

1105
00:54:11,920 --> 00:54:13,699
[SPEAKER_00] i ovo je jako bitno

1106
00:54:13,699 --> 00:54:14,719
[SPEAKER_00] da budete pozorni,

1107
00:54:14,719 --> 00:54:16,300
[SPEAKER_00] jako je čest danas

1108
00:54:16,300 --> 00:54:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] kod duhovnih ljudi.

1109
00:54:17,559 --> 00:54:20,699
[SPEAKER_00] A Sveti Bernard ga naziva ovako

1110
00:54:20,699 --> 00:54:23,719
[SPEAKER_00] obrana vlastitih pogrešaka

1111
00:54:23,719 --> 00:54:24,679
[SPEAKER_00] nepriznavanjem.

1112
00:54:24,679 --> 00:54:28,760
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ti si mogo iskoristiti

1113
00:54:28,760 --> 00:54:30,199
[SPEAKER_00] tu priliku,

1114
00:54:30,199 --> 00:54:31,780
[SPEAKER_00] čak i ako ti je možda

1115
00:54:31,780 --> 00:54:33,360
[SPEAKER_00] neka i nepravda nanesena

1116
00:54:33,360 --> 00:54:35,820
[SPEAKER_00] i možda si pretjerano napadnut,

1117
00:54:35,820 --> 00:54:37,179
[SPEAKER_00] da se vratiš Bogu

1118
00:54:37,179 --> 00:54:38,659
[SPEAKER_00] i da se vratiš u bratski odnos.

1119
00:54:38,659 --> 00:54:40,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ali najčešće, pošto je oholost

1120
