[SPEAKER_00] već djelovala u tebi,

1121
00:54:41,840 --> 00:54:44,380
[SPEAKER_00] ti ulaziš u opravdavanje.

1122
00:54:44,380 --> 00:54:46,059
[SPEAKER_00] Sveti Bernard kaže,

1123
00:54:46,059 --> 00:54:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] ok, pošto je greh javan,

1124
00:54:48,000 --> 00:54:48,940
[SPEAKER_00] ne možeš reći

1125
00:54:48,940 --> 00:54:49,920
[SPEAKER_00] nisam to učinio,

1126
00:54:49,920 --> 00:54:51,199
[SPEAKER_00] ali ćeš reći

1127
00:54:51,199 --> 00:54:52,820
[SPEAKER_00] nisam postupio veoma zlo,

1128
00:54:52,820 --> 00:54:54,639
[SPEAKER_00] to nije bilo s lošom nakanom

1129
00:54:54,639 --> 00:54:56,639
[SPEAKER_00] i onda počinješ vlastitu obremu.

1130
00:54:57,119 --> 00:54:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono kad si u oholosti,

1131
