1139
00:55:12,059 --> 00:55:13,420
[SPEAKER_00] Tok ima danas jako puno

1140
00:55:13,420 --> 00:55:14,679
[SPEAKER_00] u duhovnim krugovima

1141
00:55:14,679 --> 00:55:16,940
[SPEAKER_00] i to je meni ogavno.

1142
00:55:16,940 --> 00:55:19,400
