1146
00:55:23,980 --> 00:55:26,760
[SPEAKER_00] A to se stalno događa.

1147
00:55:26,760 --> 00:55:31,119
[SPEAKER_00] I sad, umjesto da uđeš u molitvu

1148
00:55:31,119 --> 00:55:32,639
