1149
00:55:32,639 --> 00:55:35,320
[SPEAKER_00] dajte ovaj bežići mi.

1150
00:55:35,320 --> 00:55:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ja neću glumiti da se razumijem.

1151
00:55:42,059 --> 00:55:42,579
[SPEAKER_00] u tehniku.

1152
00:55:42,579 --> 00:55:45,739
[SPEAKER_00] Je li ovako bolje?

1153
00:55:45,739 --> 00:55:50,659
[SPEAKER_00] 1, 2, 2, 2.

1154
00:55:50,659 --> 00:55:56,000
