[SPEAKER_00] kod osobe

1160
00:56:06,619 --> 00:56:08,619
[SPEAKER_00] koja je na vrhuncu

1161
00:56:08,619 --> 00:56:09,800
[SPEAKER_00] svijetovnog uspjeha.

1162
00:56:09,800 --> 00:56:11,699
[SPEAKER_00] Sad pazite,

1163
00:56:12,059 --> 00:56:14,179
[SPEAKER_00] pošto je oholoskriveni grijeh srca,

1164
00:56:14,179 --> 00:56:15,480
[SPEAKER_00] sve ove faze

1165
