[SPEAKER_00] koji žive oko tebe.

1169
00:56:21,559 --> 00:56:23,059
[SPEAKER_00] I često,

1170
00:56:23,059 --> 00:56:24,420
[SPEAKER_00] ako si tu radi o nekom

1171
00:56:24,420 --> 00:56:25,639
