[SPEAKER_00] neke svijetovne moći,

1179
00:56:36,719 --> 00:56:37,619
[SPEAKER_00] kad te svi hvale,

1180
00:56:37,619 --> 00:56:39,460
[SPEAKER_00] kad imaš veliki broj sljedbenika

1181
00:56:39,460 --> 00:56:41,320
[SPEAKER_00] i tad se ti polako

1182
