[SPEAKER_00] kada je bio onaj veliki progon

1197
00:57:07,440 --> 00:57:08,679
[SPEAKER_00] i preispitivanje

1198
00:57:08,679 --> 00:57:11,460
[SPEAKER_00] vezano uz našeg prvog duhovnika

1199
00:57:11,460 --> 00:57:12,940
[SPEAKER_00] 2019. godine,

1200
00:57:12,940 --> 00:57:15,059
[SPEAKER_00] pa naslovnice jednih novina,

1201
00:57:15,059 --> 00:57:15,619
[SPEAKER_00] pa drugih,

1202
00:57:15,619 --> 00:57:16,860
[SPEAKER_00] pa novinari dolaze.

1203
00:57:17,820 --> 00:57:18,539
[SPEAKER_00] To se dogodilo

1204
