[SPEAKER_00] ljudski gledano vrlo jaka.

1206
00:57:22,380 --> 00:57:24,179
[SPEAKER_00] Počela je rast,

1207
00:57:24,179 --> 00:57:26,019
[SPEAKER_00] bila je često prizutna u medijima,

1208
00:57:26,019 --> 00:57:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] glaskon sila,

1209
00:57:27,000 --> 00:57:28,260
[SPEAKER_00] ovo stalno izvještava

1210
00:57:28,260 --> 00:57:29,719
[SPEAKER_00] i tad se to dogodi.

1211
00:57:29,719 --> 00:57:31,719
[SPEAKER_00] Slično se događa i nekim drugim

1212
00:57:31,719 --> 00:57:34,579
