1213
00:57:34,579 --> 00:57:36,739
[SPEAKER_00] Što Bog s tim čini zapravo?

1214
00:57:36,739 --> 00:57:39,199
[SPEAKER_00] Pa čuvajte da ne uđeš u oholost.

1215
