1218
00:57:42,579 --> 00:57:45,280
[SPEAKER_00] koji sad počinje javno djelovanje

1219
00:57:45,280 --> 00:57:46,199
[SPEAKER_00] o kupe mase

1220
00:57:46,199 --> 00:57:47,920
[SPEAKER_00] i sad čudiš se

1221
00:57:47,920 --> 00:57:48,920
[SPEAKER_00] ko...

1222
00:57:48,920 --> 00:57:50,239
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, opet neću reći.

1223
00:57:50,239 --> 00:57:53,119
[SPEAKER_00] Tom crkva me preispituje.

1224
00:57:53,119 --> 00:57:54,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ma nemoj.

1225
00:57:54,860 --> 00:57:56,320
[SPEAKER_00] Pa to je dužnost crkve.

1226
00:57:56,320 --> 00:57:59,380
[SPEAKER_00] Pa naravno da ćete preispitati.

1227
00:57:59,380 --> 00:58:01,039
[SPEAKER_00] Pa mora zbog toga.

1228
00:58:01,039 --> 00:58:02,820
[SPEAKER_00] Vjer postaje masovno.

1229
00:58:02,820 --> 00:58:04,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ne postoji nijedan svetac.

1230
00:58:04,800 --> 00:58:05,920
[SPEAKER_00] Zgledajte Padre Pija

1231
00:58:05,920 --> 00:58:08,940
