[SPEAKER_00] i u našim slučajevima

1246
00:58:33,619 --> 00:58:34,900
[SPEAKER_00] i u mnogim drugima.

1247
00:58:34,900 --> 00:58:37,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ali opet,

1248
00:58:37,019 --> 00:58:39,039
[SPEAKER_00] ni lažna optužba se ne događa

1249
