[SPEAKER_00] Da li je Isusov križni put

1252
00:58:44,960 --> 00:58:45,980
[SPEAKER_00] i smrti i raspeče

1253
00:58:45,980 --> 00:58:47,659
[SPEAKER_00] se dogodilo s Božjim dopuštenjem?

1254
00:58:47,659 --> 00:58:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Je.

1255
00:58:49,000 --> 00:58:52,659
[SPEAKER_00] Da li je ta optužba bila lažna?

1256
00:58:52,659 --> 00:58:53,300
[SPEAKER_00] Pa je.

1257
00:58:53,300 --> 00:58:57,360
[SPEAKER_00] Tako i Bog može dopustiti

1258
00:58:57,360 --> 00:58:58,639
[SPEAKER_00] da se nešto dogodi,

1259
00:58:58,639 --> 00:59:00,639
[SPEAKER_00] iako naravno da to nije dobro.

1260
00:59:00,639 --> 00:59:04,260
[SPEAKER_00] I zato mislim da je jako bitno

1261
00:59:04,260 --> 00:59:06,159
