[SPEAKER_00] molim da zbog nevolja

1282
00:59:41,460 --> 00:59:42,420
[SPEAKER_00] ne klonu duhom.

1283
00:59:42,460 --> 00:59:44,440
[SPEAKER_00] neka znaju

1284
